	   <tr><td colspan=2>"a twink's skills suffer because of the higher AC they have than they should have. The mobs won't hit you. If the mobs don't hit you, your defense wont go up. "<br><br>You should do a bit more research.<br>Even if the mob MISSES you, your defense still takes a check and goes up. Higher AC just means better protection, but defense will STILL go up as normal.<br><br>Now, if they have a weapon that drops everything in sight in 1 hit, that makes your defense suffer, because you are not being attacked nearly as much.<br><br>*not meant as a flame, just clearing that up*<br><br>Heh, Whaddya know, my first board post. *cheers*<br><br>24 High Elf Cleric O' Da 7th Hammer!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
